{"tid":1535384,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[連仔入] 一日一Post 問題","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:01:08.000Z","uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abff21fe84c18993b213fe4099097026492da615","tid":1535384,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"朋友有啲嘢想做，求為一Account 解放一日一Post。連仔有無可能做到？"},{"pid":"ea51111ea1febbb3d1ef494775be08ca026d8a38","tid":1535384,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58537e043068b7455c5860670d50a05061a83582","tid":1535384,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eab76b19a5b1a18ba533428209cac3d52e1d7ded","tid":1535384,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n5. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n6. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n7. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n8. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n9. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"f460a6eb7ae4ee54920547739084fa2ca3a61e4f","tid":1535384,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"借非P牌會員account，有的話"},{"pid":"a0eda5fa95daaf1d44599dc2b895305be1508443","tid":1535384,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460a6eb7ae4ee54920547739084fa2ca3a61e4f","tid":1535384,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"借非P牌會員account，有的話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"就係無，所以先想連仔開一開俾一個Account"},{"pid":"07fad8dd01c76c881bbf0bd92eec813902ef1ccd","tid":1535384,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0eda5fa95daaf1d44599dc2b895305be1508443","tid":1535384,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460a6eb7ae4ee54920547739084fa2ca3a61e4f","tid":1535384,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"借非P牌會員account，有的話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"就係無，所以先想連仔開一開俾一個Account"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56814e4b5d54d53d2bf0d42e05bc